snippet.title: Stronger - Strength By The Numbers
snippet.description:
We all need some motivation from time to time. Hopefully seeing the possibilities of human limits can motivate you to be stronger in whatever area you want to conquer! Real strength comes from within. 

I make all of my data visualizations from scratch from open data sets. Here's where I got the data for this video: https://www.kaggle.com/open-powerlifting/powerlifting-database/data

That catchy tune in the background :) https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=myeYiTQ0Akc

This is a little different from my other data videos, hopefully you all enjoyed this one. What area do you want to be stronger in? Let me know, I'm excited to hear your responses!

If you enjoyed this video please leave a like and consider subscribing!
